    <span class = "question">Q: </span>How is the payment made?
    </p>
    <p class = "faq">
    <span class = "answer">A: </span>Payment by bank cards is carried out through Alfa-Bank CJSC.
<p>Cards of international payment systems VISA, MasterCard,
