<p>The card data is entered on the secure authorization page of the bank.</p>
<p>When paying with Apple Pay, select a card from the Wallet application, use a password
or other authentication method, depending on which method is selected in the application.</p>
<p>When placing an order using Samsung Pay, click "Pay Samsung Pay", enter your
Samsung Account and confirm the purchase on your smartphone (by fingerprint, iris or
Samsung Pay PIN).</p>
<p>The personal information you provide (for example, name, address, phone number, e-mail,
bank card number, etc.) is confidential and not subject to disclosure.</p>
<p>The card data is transmitted only in encrypted form and is not stored on this Internet resource.</p>
    </p>
