    <p class = "faq">
    <span class = "question">Q: </span>How can I return my money?
    </p>
    <p class = "faq">
    <span class = "answer">A: </span>When paying with a bank payment card, a cash refund is not allowed. Settlements with the consumer upon return of the amount of money paid for the goods, upon termination of the contract for the performance of work (provision of services) are carried out in the same form in which payment for the goods, work (services) was made, unless otherwise provided by the agreement of the parties. The refund procedure is regulated by the rules of payment systems. The procedure for returning goods is regulated by the Law of the Republic of Belarus of January 9, 2002 N 90-3 "On Consumer Rights Protection".

<p>The consumer has the right to refuse the goods within 14 (fourteen) days from the date of transfer of the goods to him;</p>
<p>The consumer has the right to unilaterally refuse to execute the contract on performance of work (provision of services) on condition of payment to the contractor of the expenses actually incurred by him, unless otherwise provided by law.</p>
<p>The consumer's demand for the exchange or return of a quality product is subject to satisfaction if the product was not in use, its consumer properties are preserved and there is evidence of its purchase from this seller.</p>
<p>The list of non-food products of proper quality that are not subject to exchange and return is approved by the Government of the Republic of Belarus.</p>

<p>To return funds to a bank payment card, you must fill out an "Application for a refund of funds" and send it to the email address возврат@домен.by . The refund will be made to the bank payment card within 7 (seven) calendar days from the date of receipt of the "Application for refund" by the Company. The refund amount will be equal to the purchase amount</p>

<p>In order to refund funds for transactions carried out with errors, it is necessary to apply with a written application and an attachment of checks / receipts confirming the erroneous write-off. This application must be sent by e-mail support@beauty-academy.by.</p>
